odd.p:
Notebook used during student years. Includes notes, drafts of essays and poems (some later published in 
                           Fifty Years and Other Poems
                        ). With a typed list of poems laid in.

scopecontent.p:
Contains drafts and final versions of poems (some later published in 
                           Fifty Years and Other Poems
                        ). Poems included are: "Since You Went Away"; "The Color Sergeant"; "Dat Gal O'Mine"; "Tunk"; "The Rivals"; "Answer to Prayer"; "National Hymn" [Lift Every Voice]; "The Black Mammy"; "When First We Met"; "You'se Sweet to Yo' Mammy Jes de Same"; "The Glory of the Day Was in Her Face"; "Two Sonnets to Horace Bumstead"; "Sonnet Before a Painting"; "Louisiana Lize."
